# 1. kubevirt vm固定IP

##   1.1 功能

创建虚拟机固定IP

必须支持指定网络，包括sriov资源池（注解）

非必须指定IP（注解）



![图片](data:image/png;base64,)



##   1.2 vm 指定 annotations

前提：在部署完sriov网络模块后，已经生产了vf池mecdev.com/intel2v2nics和nad sriov-network-100-100-100-0-24。nad的内容为以下

```
apiVersion: k8s.cni.cncf.io/v1
kind: NetworkAttachmentDefinition
metadata:
  annotations:
    k8s.v1.cni.cncf.io/resourceName: mecdev.com/intel2v2nics
  name: sriov-network-100-100-100-0-24
  namespace: sriov-network-operator
spec:
  config: '{ "cniVersion":"0.3.1", "name":"sriov-network-100-100-100-0-24","type":"sriov","vlan":0,"vlanQoS":0,"ipam":{"type":"whereabouts","range":"100.100.100.2-100.100.100.254/24","gateway":"100.100.100.1"}
    }'

```

meo创建vm时会带有以下注解

```
k8s.v1.cni.cncf.io/sriovnetworks: '[{"subnet": "100.100.100.0/24", "resourcename":"mecdev.com/intel2v2nics","name":"sriov-network-100-100-100-0-24","ipaddress": "100.100.100.100", "gateway", "100.100.100.1"}]'
```

##   1.3 获取IP 以及 mac地址（数组）

```
k8s.v1.cni.cncf.io/sriovnetworks: '[{"subnet": "100.100.100.0/24", "resourcename":"mecdev.com/intel2v2nics", "name":"sriov-network-100-100-100-24","ipaddress": "100.100.100.100", "gateway", "100.100.100.1"}]'
```

vm根据网络信息，配置cloud-init

```
   - cloudInitNoCloud:

          networkData: |
              version: 2
              ethernets:
                  enp1s0:                    #不同os image取名不一样enp1s0或者eth0
                    dhcp4: true
                    dhcp4-overrides:
                      route-metric: 200
                    routes:
                      - to: 10.233.0.0/24
                        via: 169.254.1.1
                      - to: 172.16.236.0/24
                        via: 169.254.1.1
                  sriov-net:
                      set-name: sriovnet
                      addresses:
                         - 100.100.100.100/24
                      gateway4: 100.100.100.1
                      nameservers:
                        addresses:
                            - 114.114.114.114
                        search: []
```



# 二. pod固定IP


![图片](data:image/png;base64,)


##   2.1 创建 deploy /stateful 指定注解

```
k8s.v1.cni.cncf.io/sriovnetworks: '[{"subnet": "100.100.100.0/24", "resourcename":"mecdev.com/intel2v2nics"}]'
```

##   2.2 获取IP 以及 mac地址（数组）

```
k8s.v1.cni.cncf.io/sriovnetworks: '[{"subnet": "100.100.100.0/24", "resourcename":"mecdev.com/intel2v2nics", "ippool" : [{"name":"sriov-n3-static-100-100-100-100","ipaddress": "100.100.100.100","gateway":"100.100.100.1"}, {"name":"sriov-n3-static-100-100-100-200","ipaddress": "100.100.100.200", "gateway":"100.100.100.1"}]}]'
```

##   2.3 创建 NRD

```
apiVersion: k8s.cni.cncf.io/v1

kind: NetworkAttachmentDefinition

metadata:

  annotations:

    k8s.v1.cni.cncf.io/resourceName: mecdev.com/intel2nics

  name: sriov-n3-static-100-100-100-100

  namespace: sriov-network-operator

spec:

  config: '{ "cniVersion":"0.3.1", "name":"sriov-n3-static-100-100-100-100","type":"sriov","vlan":0,"vlanQoS":0,"ipam":{"type":"static","addresses":[{"address":"100.100.100.100/24","gateway":"100.100.100.1"}],"dns":{"nameservers":["114.114.114.114"]}}}'
```

### 2.4 pod使用 NRD

为 pod 选择个未占用的 IP，添加注解到 pod

```
k8s.v1.cni.cncf.io/networks: '[{"name": "sriov-n3-static-100-100-100-100", "namespace":"sriov-network-operator"}]'
```
